611
00:35:04.300 --> 00:35:08.140
And third, I'll highlight how targeting A20 unlocks a novel RIP3 CASP1

612
00:35:08.260 --> 00:35:09.200
pathway in TILs.

613
00:35:12.960 --> 00:35:16.720
Our story begins with a genome-wide CRISPR knockout screen to identify

614
00:35:16.740 --> 00:35:20.720
suppressors of exhausted T cell persistence, for which we designed a

615
00:35:20.780 --> 00:35:24.340
