619
00:35:31.100 --> 00:35:33.570
TNFAIP3, or A20,

620
00:35:34.380 --> 00:35:37.520
suggesting that A20 is a critical enforcer of exhaustion.

621
00:35:39.760 --> 00:35:43.440
