623
00:35:48.580 --> 00:35:50.500
In A375 melanoma

624
00:35:52.340 --> 00:35:56.100
treated with Cas9-edited NY-ESO-1 specific TCR T

625
00:35:56.200 --> 00:35:58.540
cells, A20 knockout in orange

626
00:35:59.660 --> 00:36:03.040
dramatically improved tumor suppression compared to controls in blue

627
00:36:04.980 --> 00:36:07.820
