631
00:36:21.460 --> 00:36:22.580
solid and liquid

632
00:36:22.680 --> 00:36:26.460
tumors.We next aim to

633
00:36:26.500 --> 00:36:29.780
understand A20 biology in exhausted T cells.

634
00:36:30.360 --> 00:36:34.200
A20 is a multifunctional enzyme that can add, remove, or

635
00:36:34.340 --> 00:36:38.310
bind to ubiquitin on target proteins to regulate their activity.

636
00:36:39.500 --> 00:36:43.470
It's best known as a suppressor of NF-kappa B, and

637
00:36:43.500 --> 00:36:47.040
several studies have suggested that A20 restrains TIL

638
00:36:47.100 --> 00:36:50.220
activity, though the underlying mechanisms were not defined.

639
00:36:52.480 --> 00:36:56.280
We first aimed to dissect which domain within

640
00:36:56.340 --> 00:36:58.740
the multifunctional A20 protein

641
00:36:59.620 --> 00:37:02.240
was responsible for tumor immunity.

642
00:37:04.380 --> 00:37:07.880
After using a protein large language model and a base editor tiling screen, we

643
00:37:07.940 --> 00:37:11.620
narrowed the likely candidates to the OTU deubiquitinase,

644
00:37:12.340 --> 00:37:15.840
the zinc finger four ubiquitin ligase, and the zinc finger

645
00:37:16.000 --> 00:37:18.320
seven ubiquitin binding domains.

646
00:37:19.660 --> 00:37:23.220
We then leveraged our panel of germline knock-in mice with A20

647
00:37:23.260 --> 00:37:26.240
domain-specific inactivating mutations.

648
00:37:27.460 --> 00:37:30.450
When we challenged with MC38 syngeneic tumors,

649
00:37:31.460 --> 00:37:35.240
mice homozygous for the OTU or zinc finger four

650
00:37:35.260 --> 00:37:36.000
mutations,

651
00:37:36.880 --> 00:37:37.500
in red,

652
00:37:39.140 --> 00:37:42.040
were no different than their wild type counterparts, in blue,

653
00:37:43.020 --> 00:37:45.000
in terms of tumor growth and survival.

654
00:37:46.720 --> 00:37:50.470
However, mice homozygous for the zinc finger seven mutation showed

655
00:37:50.480 --> 00:37:53.660
dramatically improved tumor control and survival,

656
00:37:54.810 --> 00:37:56.460
and nearly half cleared their tumors.

657
00:37:58.660 --> 00:38:02.600
And we have data not shown that confirms the importance of CD8 intrinsic zinc

658
00:38:02.660 --> 00:38:03.140
finger seven.

