660
00:38:10.160 --> 00:38:13.850
instead of Cas9 to generate a missense mutation that

661
00:38:13.860 --> 00:38:15.840
precisely inactivates zinc finger seven.

662
00:38:16.780 --> 00:38:20.340
For comparison, we also used base editing to generate A20 knockout via

663
00:38:20.400 --> 00:38:21.520
