666
00:38:30.520 --> 00:38:34.180
with base editing greatly enhanced ACT activity against

667
00:38:34.300 --> 00:38:37.200
A375 melanoma and Nalm6 leukemia.

668
00:38:38.350 --> 00:38:42.000
Thus, zinc finger seven is a powerful and precise target for

669
00:38:42.040 --> 00:38:43.509
