This strategy revealed a striking differential in perforin

713
00:41:11.280 --> 00:41:15.060
content within brefeldin-treated zinc finger seven, but

714
00:41:15.160 --> 00:41:18.720
not wild type Ttex, suggesting zinc finger seven

715
00:41:18.780 --> 00:41:22.580
Ttex are robustly degranulating in vivo and

716
