723
00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:50.280
Taken together, these results indicate that A20 differentially regulates

724
00:41:50.340 --> 00:41:53.760
cytokine versus perforin release, the latter at the step of

725
00:41:53.880 --> 00:41:55.740
