742
00:42:56.800 --> 00:42:59.660
and reversed the Ttex degranulation phenotype.

743
00:43:01.740 --> 00:43:05.280
In addition, caspase-1 deficiency phenocopied RIP3

744
00:43:05.300 --> 00:43:08.800
