00:47:06.200 --> 00:47:09.660
downstream of TNF, have you looked at

811
00:47:09.740 --> 00:47:13.580
upstream signals like tumor necrosis factor or FAS as

812
00:47:13.600 --> 00:47:17.480
potential-- Is there some rewiring of that signaling that's going on here

813
00:47:17.500 --> 00:47:21.460
