00:47:39.440 --> 00:47:41.120
would be really fascinating.

821
00:47:41.920 --> 00:47:42.320
But there's

822
00:47:43.140 --> 00:47:44.780
kind of a lot of signals to explore.

823
00:47:45.400 --> 00:47:48.700
Have you transcriptionally profiled the cells after A20 knockout?

824
00:47:49.340 --> 00:47:51.400
Yeah. We have.

825
00:47:53.500 --> 00:47:55.680
We have just done it in the human rep stem.

826
00:47:57.140 --> 00:47:57.600
And

827
00:47:59.480 --> 00:48:03.140
the biggest signal we get is a major metabolic

828
00:48:03.240 --> 00:48:04.580
shift towards that

829
00:48:05.800 --> 00:48:09.630
disfavors OXPHOS, and so we're trying to make sense of that because

