00:48:38.480 --> 00:48:42.120
the main thing that we didn't expect was the disfavoring of

839
00:48:42.180 --> 00:48:42.720
OXPHOS.

840
00:48:43.588 --> 00:48:44.388
I see. Okay.

841
00:48:44.548 --> 00:48:44.648
Yeah.

